{
  "stem": "15578.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we spent a lot of time-- like I have some time after school, Saturday mostly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we met together, at night, sometimes until about 9, 10 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we had to go home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the young boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everybody is saying this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I think we had the nicest young boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was just sport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We played soccer, we played ping pong.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had-- had it called the JTGS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The most time I spend there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all the young boys and girls there too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's called-- in Polish it's called [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish Organization Sport Fed-- that's what I did translate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did play everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I even played basketball.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The best, what I was very, very good, was ping-pong.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I played soccer, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "JTGS.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had our own soccer club.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we played a lot of teams.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had one German team was called Victoria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there was [INAUDIBLE] Then there was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was like to say that was a club like the NDP, was called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then was Hakoah, and one was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, very much so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they could knock your feet, they did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if we won, they could fight after the game with us too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, a lot of times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I recall that one time was played [INAUDIBLE] and from Lodz, a club called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they did play for a higher-- like there was divided A, B, C, and to go in a higher category.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that time, the [INAUDIBLE] won.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was a very, very bad that time, the fighting, after the game.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
